{"metadata":{"externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNMapView(im)setTargetCoordinate:animated:","symbolKind":"method","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"setTargetCoordinate:animated:","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"setTargetCoordinate:animated:","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"setTargetCoordinate:animated:","kind":"identifier"}],"modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"platforms":[{"beta":false,"deprecated":true,"unavailable":false}],"remoteSource":{"fileName":"MLNMapView.h","url":"https:\/\/github.com\/maplibre\/maplibre-native\/blob\/main\/platform\/ios\/src\/MLNMapView.h#L775"},"roleHeading":"Instance Method"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView"]]},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"kind":"symbol","variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview\/settargetcoordinate:animated:"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"text":"- (","kind":"text"},{"text":"void","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:v"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"setTargetCoordinate:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"CLLocationCoordinate2D","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:@S@CLLocationCoordinate2D"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"targetCoordinate","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"animated:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@BOOL","text":"BOOL"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"animated"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"platforms":["iOS"]}]},{"parameters":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The target coordinate to fit within the viewport."}]}],"name":"targetCoordinate"},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"YES"},{"type":"text","text":", the map animates to fit the target within the map"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"view. If "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NO"},{"type":"text","text":", the map fits the target instantaneously."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"animated"}],"kind":"parameters"},{"content":[{"type":"heading","text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"By default, the target coordinate is set to an invalid coordinate, indicating"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"that there is no target. In course tracking mode, the target forms one of two"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"foci in the viewport, the other being the user location annotation. Typically,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the target is set to a destination or waypoint in a real-time navigation scene."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"As the user annotation moves toward the target, the map automatically zooms in"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to fit both foci optimally within the viewport."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This method has no effect if the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"userTrackingMode"},{"type":"text","text":" property is set to a value"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"other than "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNUserTrackingMode\/MLNUserTrackingModeFollowWithCourse","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"To specify a completion handler to execute after the animation finishes, use"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the "},{"code":"-setTargetCoordinate:animated:completionHandler:","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" method."}]}],"kind":"content"}],"abstract":[{"text":"Deprecated. Sets the geographic coordinate that is the subject of observation as","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the user location is being tracked, with an optional transition animation.","type":"text"}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView\/setTargetCoordinate:animated:"},"sections":[],"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapView/setTargetCoordinate:animated:":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView\/setTargetCoordinate:animated:","type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Deprecated. Sets the geographic coordinate that is the subject of observation as"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the user location is being tracked, with an optional transition animation."}],"fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"- "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"setTargetCoordinate:animated:"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"setTargetCoordinate:animated:"}],"kind":"symbol","title":"setTargetCoordinate:animated:","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview\/settargetcoordinate:animated:","role":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapView":{"role":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"An interactive, customizable map view with an interface similar to the one","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"provided by Apple’s MapKit.","type":"text"}],"fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNMapView"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview","kind":"symbol","title":"MLNMapView","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView","type":"topic"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNUserTrackingMode/MLNUserTrackingModeFollowWithCourse":{"type":"topic","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnusertrackingmode\/mlnusertrackingmodefollowwithcourse","abstract":[],"fragments":[{"text":"MLNUserTrackingModeFollowWithCourse","kind":"identifier"}],"title"